WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.866 --> 00:00:02.466
Such a ruthless person

2
00:00:02.700 --> 00:00:04.466
Don't teach you to bring justice

3
00:00:04.466 --> 00:00:06.566
It's so hard to understand that I hate you in my heart

4
00:00:07.766 --> 00:00:10.066
I'm just taking his place

5
00:00:10.266 --> 00:00:11.866
You can't cure me

6
00:00:12.100 --> 00:00:13.000
Besides

7
00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:16.833
At that time, you took the initiative to beg me to stay in the Lu family

8
00:00:17.166 --> 00:00:18.633
Is that really the case?

9
00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:20.866
The boss has woken up

10
00:00:21.866 --> 00:00:24.866
Impossible, I clearly know what

11
00:00:25.566 --> 00:00:27.066
Killed by you

12
00:00:27.466 --> 00:00:28.566
What do you mean?

13
00:00:28.600 --> 00:00:30.600
You don't think you're just going to change the topic.

14
00:00:30.600 --> 00:00:32.500
It can take my attention away

15
00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:34.400
When did you find out?

16
00:00:34.400 --> 00:00:36.266
From the moment you open the door

17
00:00:36.266 --> 00:00:39.000
I can smell the strong smell of blood on you

18
00:00:39.566 --> 00:00:41.666
Let the secretary come into the room to check

19
00:00:42.466 --> 00:00:45.100
You will learn that in order to cut weeds and eradicate roots

20
00:00:45.133 --> 00:00:47.600
Killed your own father with his own hands

21
00:00:48.333 --> 00:00:49.666
Nonsense

22
00:00:49.666 --> 00:00:51.866
How could I possibly hurt my biological father?

23
00:00:52.133 --> 00:00:55.066
People like this are unscrupulous and shameless

24
00:00:55.066 --> 00:00:57.366
I can't keep you in the Lu family

25
00:00:57.466 --> 00:00:58.666
Take him away

